node.text:
The smell of the octane, sound of the motor and sight of beautiful rides can only mean one thing… you’re in the Power & Performance lab at UTI.
 
In this 9-week program, you’ll learn how to complete a full engine teardown, blueprint and rebuild. You’ll even have the opportunity to drop your engine into a T bucket and run it on the dyno!
 
This program is offered as part of the 51-week Automotive Technology program. UTI teamed up with industry leader Roush Yates Engines to develop curriculum based on the modern racing experience. 
 
Power & Performance is available at 10 campus locations: 
 
●  Avondale, AZ
●  Dallas/Fort Worth, TX
●  Exton, PA
●  Bloomfield, NJ
●  Houston, TX
●  Lisle, IL
●  Long Beach, CA
●  Orlando, FL

●  Rancho Cucamonga, CA
●  Sacramento, CA
 
#AutoTechnician #Automotive #PowerandPerformance #Cars #FollowYourDreams #Racing #RoushYates #Engine #EngineRebuild #DynoTune #CarTuning

node.title: Learn How to Tune a Car in UTI’s Power & Performance Lab 🔥
